title: [LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan 716 - Dancing Demon in the Noh
description:
[LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan 716 - Dancing Demon in the Noh Mask Mansion (Part 1)


A mysterious letter warns of a life in danger, so Mouri, Ran and Conan go to investigate. But these three "demons" of the museum keep trying to assassinate the owner! Just what is going on?!
